longBusinessSummary: Jiayin Group Inc. operates as an online individual finance platform that connects individual investors and individual borrowers in China. It operates a secure and open platform that facilitates transparent, secure, and fast connections between investors and borrowers. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
address2: 26th Floor Youyou Century Plaza 428 South Yanggao Road, Pudong New Area
